Title: Protein Kera Cysteine Hair Styler
Description: Protein Kera Cysteine Treatment is completely free of formaldehyde producing ingredients. Cysteine is one of the many amino acids that combine to form keratin, allowing for powerful moisture retention. Cysteine Protein blend, which reacts with hydrogen and oxygen, causing the molecules to attach themselves to each other and filling protein in the gaps of the hair shaft. This is what eliminates the frizz, while adding weight to the hair shaft causing the smoother, straighter effect. It helps in repairing dry, damage and frizzy hair. The process of the Protein Kera Cysteine Treatment is very simple. Your Salon provider will first wash your hair with the Protein Kera Clarifying Shampoo in preparation for the treatment. Then your hair is blast dried free style until 100% dry with medium heat. Your hair is sectioned to apply the treatment with a brush as you would apply hair color. The treatment is left in the hair for aprox 20-30 minutes. The hair is then blast dried using medium heat to completly dry the product. Finally the hair is flat ironed using very small sections making your hair very smooth, silky, and shiny. It is as simple as 1 - 2 - 3. It is Ideal for Unisex.Its effect last for 3-5 months and its gives 4 times smooth , soft , shiny , silky and relaxes the hair upto 70-80%. You can visit your near Salon or Do it yourself at home.

Title: Sunprotek Gel - SPF 30 PA+++(50 Gram)
Description: Managing sun exposure is a serious business, with increasing awareness Sunscreens have ceased to be just a cosmetic, today it is a well established fact that your sunscreen must be tested and certified for all the label claims.Sunprotek 50+ Gel is the next step towards offering you a truly world class formulation at affordable price.In fact Sunprotek 50+ Gel is a composition of carefully chosen ingredients that have their unique individual role in making Sunprotek 50+ Gel a truly protecting, nurturing and nourishing sunscreen. Sunprotek 50+ Gel is the next generation sunscreen that comes with the unique W/O/W encapsulation (nano) technology thatHelps in forming a very consistent formulation with very even spreadability that offers uniform protection , which is not so with other sunscreens. Reduction of absorption of sunscreen chemicals in the skin???There is a growing concern that the sunscreen agents applied to the skin must stay on the skin only & not get absorbed into the circulation where they are not required.The following data obtained from an in vitro experiment demonstrates that W/O/W encapsulation reduces the absorption of sunscreen chemicals into the skin.Whereby 3 samples? Sample A: Cream Base only ? Sample B : OMC 5% cream ? Sample C : Sunprotek Gel with W/O/W encapsulationwere applied to artificial skin and samples of the artificial body fluid were measured for UV absorbance. Sample with the least absorbance of UV rays in body fluid would be the most appropriate formulation. Sunprotek 50+ Gel contains the followingOMC: Octyl methoxycinnamate or octinoxate, a non PABA sunscreen agent, used in suncreens to absorb UV-B rays from the sun, protecting the skin from damage. It is also used to reduce the appearance of scars. Octyl methoxycinnamate and other sun screening agents do not penetrate the outer skin in sufficient concentration to cause any significant toxicity to the underlying human keratinocytes.Benzophenone-3, or Oxybenzone, primarily functions as a photostabilizer and sunscreen. Benzophenone-3 is classified as a "chemical" sunscreen agent. Benzophenone-3 absorbs UVB and short UVA rays. By absorbing UV rays, it also helps preserve the integrity of other cosmetic ingredients, preventing their deterioration under the sun.Avobenzone : is the only chemical that absorbs the whole UVA spectrum from 310-400 nm. This makes it an ideal additive to any sunscreen formulation.PEG12 Dimethicone: Acts as a humectant & emollient imparts a soft and silky feel to the skin. It also has Antiperspirant/Deodorant Properties.Allantoin : keeps the skin soft, smooth, and healthy. Allantoin also helps protect the skin against various irritantsVitamin E : has positive effects against skin ageing due to ultraviolet light, and protects cells by reducing itchiness and free-radical damage.Chamomile Extract : Chamomile has antioxidant, antimicrobial activities, and a potent anti-inflammatory actionAloe Vera Extract : Humidifies, smooths and reaffirms the skin, eliminates the ageing spots, and also acts as astringent, solar filter.Phospholipids: Addition of phospholipid base enhances the nurturing and nourishing qualities of Sunprotek 30+/50+ Gel as, the phospholipids are natural components of cell walls and when supplied from outside they are readily accepted by the body. Phospholipids have a:Repairing action: Because of stronger attraction to the stratum corneum, it helps in faster restoration of the lipidic barrier of damaged skin.Protective action: Phospholipids form a film which protects the surface of the skin from damage responsible for irritation.Anti-dehydrating action : High capacity for binding water: 1 phospholipid molecule binds with 23 water molecules so it helps in enhanced retention of water in the surface and deep layers of the skin and adds to the suppleness of the skin.Summarily the phospholipids provide the following benefits to the sun damaged skin ? Restructuring ? Film forming ? Hydrating ? CalmingAcrylates C10-30 Alkyl Acrylates Cross polymer: Have a high capacity to absorb water & thus help maintain a moisturized skin. It also imparts a very soft and silky feel to the skin.Sunprotek 30+/50+ Gel were analyzed at Bio-Nest Biochem. Tech. Co. Ltd. using DAISO ULTRAVIOLET TRANSMITTANCE ANALYZER and certified for the following. Summarily Sunprotek 50+ Gel-Offers broad spectrum protection against UVA &UVB both.-Gel Formulation for excellent cosmetic acceptance.-Very suitable for oily & acne prone skin.-Phospholipids provide excellent moisturization to the skin. Microencapsulation technology has helped to-Replace traditional sunscreen-Prevent absorption of sunscreen chemicals into the skin and safely increase the residence time of sunscreen on the skin-Attain Excellent tolerability for sensitive skin-Provides HIGHER SPF i.e. better protection using less quantity of actives as compared to normal sunscreen formulations available in the market.-Leaves a refreshing & light feeling skin that breaths easily & freely post application, as compared to heavy feeling on skin that occurs with other sunscreens.-Does not flare acne outburst. Contra Indication: Hypersensitivity to any of the ingredients of the formulation.Directions for use : As directed.

Description: About this Piece:This is a handmade Bidar work of art. It is a Mango shaped box with pure silver inlay and can be used for multiple purposes.About Bidri Artwork:Bidri artwork, or Bidriware, is a metal handicraft that is made in Bidar, Karnataka. The pieces consists of a black zinc-copper alloy with intricate inlays of pure silver. Bidriware is made by traditional methods including casting, chiseling and manual polishing. Materials such as earth from the Bidar Fort, castor oil, resin, copper sulphate and ammonium chloride are used to create these works of art that are like no other.All our products are genuine and made by master artisans in Bidar. We follow fair trade practices and ensure that our craftsmen and craftswomen are treated with the respect they deserve.
